==English==
===Pronunciation===
* /Ëˆdili/

===Etymology===
Diminutive of [[deal]].

===Noun===
'''dealie''' ''(plural:'' '''[[dealies]]''')
# ''colloquial'' A thing, especially one seen as complex or having much associated with it.  

===Usage===
Sometimes used as a placeholder for an object whose name does not immediately spring to mind, as, ''Hand me that little plastic dealie.'' 

More often used with a noun in attribution, as, ''How do I set up this blog dealie?''

